# ipcmk

> Create IPC (Inter-process Communication) resources
> More information: https://manned.org/ipcmk

- Create a shared memory segment:

`ipcmk --shmem {string value: segment_size_in_bytes}`

- Create a semaphore:

`ipcmk --semaphore {string value: element_size}`

- Create a message queue:

`ipcmk --queue`

- Create a shared memory segment with specific permissions (default is 0644):

`ipcmk --shmem {string value: segment_size_in_bytes} {string value: octal_permissions}`
